94
00:09:47.670 --> 00:09:50.150
Concentrate on your concentration.

95
00:09:50.710 --> 00:09:52.790
Why do you get so excited
when you see a spinner?


96
00:09:54.470 --> 00:09:56.270
T20 generation!

97
