after he popped it.


109
00:11:40.990 --> 00:11:42.270
I missed you, Ani.

110
00:11:43.510 --> 00:11:44.830
Life is so strange...

111
00:11:45.030 --> 00:11:46.870
As kids, we spent every day together

112
00:11:47.030 --> 00:11:48.470
then suddenly life takes over

113
00:11:48.710 --> 00:11:50.430
and we go our different ways.

114
00:11:51.670 --> 00:11:52.870
And then one day,

115
00:11:54.190 --> 00:11:55.430
suddenly we meet again.

116
00:11:56.910 --> 00:11:58.630
Feels like we've been meeting every day.

117
00:12:00.310 --> 00:12:01.150
Really?

118
00:12:01.790 --> 00:12:02.830
Stop the car.

119
00:12:03.150 --> 00:12:03.830
What!

120
00:12:07.150 --> 00:12:08.350
What are you doing?

121
00:12:08.470 --> 00:12:10.110
Ani, you're spoiling my hair!

122
00:12:10.230 --> 00:12:11.550
Is this how you behave?

123
00:12:11.670 --> 00:12:12.870
What's going on?
Hitting a girl?


124
00:12:12.990 --> 00:12:14.710
The girl is hitting me, man!

125
00:12:14.910 --> 00:12:17.630
- Did I ask you for help?
- Crazy girl...


126
00:12:20.150 --> 00:12:22.390
Were you in a coma all these years,
you rascal?


127
00:12:23.390 --> 00:12:25.910
You'd follow me around
like a puppy every day


128
00:12:26.310 --> 00:12:28.510
