after moving to USA, you dog.


129
00:12:28.870 --> 00:12:29.710
Ani...

130
00:12:30.630 --> 00:12:34.430
Had to check out my options in USA.

131
00:12:38.670 --> 00:12:41.870
Now it feels like we've been meeting
every day!


132
00:12:43.710 --> 00:12:44.950
How long are you here for?

133
00:12:45.550 --> 00:12:47.150
As long as I'm alive!

134
00:12:59.950 --> 00:13:01.430
Want me to drag you in?

135
00:13:09.510 --> 00:13:10.670
Hello?

136
00:13:11.990 --> 00:13:13.310
Yes sir, this is Anina.

137
00:13:17.910 --> 00:13:19.030
Thank you, sir.

138
00:13:19.230 --> 00:13:20.110
Yes, sir.

139
00:13:20.750 --> 00:13:21.710
Granny...

140
00:13:21.830 --> 00:13:22.910
Dad!

141
00:13:23.230 --> 00:13:23.870
I made it.

142
00:13:23.990 --> 00:13:26.070
I made it to the Indian team
probables for the England tour.


143
00:13:26.870 --> 00:13:28.590
I am so proud of you.

144
00:13:29.030 --> 00:13:30.150
Granny...

145
00:13:33.070 --> 00:13:35.630
Don't cry, it's time to make
the opposition cry.


146
00:13:36.870 --> 00:13:39.270
I've fully analyzed the English bowlers.

147
00:13:39.430 --> 00:13:40.670
Their spinning department is weak.

148
00:13:40.790 --> 00:13:42.830
