152
00:13:50.030 --> 00:13:53.070
Remember Jeet, Granny?

153
00:13:56.150 --> 00:13:58.190
Puppy love still following you around?

154
00:14:00.190 --> 00:14:00.790
Come.

155
00:14:02.710 --> 00:14:04.030
Give me your hand, Ani.

156
00:14:06.430 --> 00:14:07.270
What is this?

157
00:14:07.470 --> 00:14:08.590
Superstition.

158
00:14:08.790 --> 00:14:11.030
I've been praying for three months now

159
00:14:11.150 --> 00:14:12.790
that's why she has been selected.

160
00:14:13.070 --> 00:14:15.190
This sacred thread is more powerful
than a bat.


161
00:14:15.310 --> 00:14:17.630
You'll see, she'll score a century
in her very first match!


162
00:14:17.750 --> 00:14:19.630
For that, I have to be selected
in the team first.


163
00:14:19.910 --> 00:14:21.430
This is only a list
of the probables.


164
00:14:21.790 --> 00:14:23.550
I don't know if I'll make it
to the 16.


165
00:14:24.030 --> 00:14:26.510
- I don't believe in all this rubbish.
- I believe in it.


166
00:14:26.750 --> 00:14:29.310
Bribing a God for his daughter!

167
00:14:29.550 --> 00:14:31.590
Mohinder Amarnath always kept
a red handkerchief


168
00:14:31.710 --> 00:14:33.030
in his pocket, while batting.

169
00:14:37.310 --> 00:14:40.270
And 'Dada'... Sourav Ganguly...

170
00:14:40.710 --> 00:14:42.950
would keep his guru's photo
in his pocket.


171
00:14:43.150 --> 00:14:46.310
Sachin... always wore
his left pad first.


172
00:14:46.710 --> 00:14:49.830
Legends and superstition
seem to be made for each other.


173
00:14:51.190 --> 00:14:52.630
G.R. Vishwanath?

174
00:14:53.270 --> 00:14:56.510
India's real legend, who played
before you were even born.


175
00:14:57.110 --> 00:15:01.310
To face Andy Roberts without a helmet,
you need self-belief


176
00:15:01.550 --> 00:15:02.590
not superstition!

177
00:15:04.310 --> 00:15:06.550
Keep it on only
if you score a 100.

178
00:15:07.270 --> 00:15:10.190
- You?
- Hello, Uncle... Jeet. Remember me?


179
00:15:10.590 --> 00:15:11.510
Jeet?

180
00:15:13.750 --> 00:15:16.070
Didn't Ani break your teeth once?

181
00:15:23.590 --> 00:15:24.550
Ma'am is here.

182
00:15:24.790 --> 00:15:27.030
I'm so sorry. Too much traffic.

183
00:15:27.230 --> 00:15:28.790
Don't apologize, ma'am.

184
00:15:29.030 --> 00:15:30.950
The Chairman of Selectors can be late.

185
00:15:34.550 --> 00:15:35.070
Hello.

186
00:15:35.190 --> 00:15:37.950
Coach, after the 15-day camp...
what's your feeling?


187
00:15:38.230 --> 00:15:39.710
Who's fit? Who isn't?

188
00:15:39.830 --> 00:15:41.630
Tell us and make our jobs easier.

189
00:15:41.790 --> 00:15:43.270
Sorry, ma'am, all the girls
are super fit.


190
00:15:43.390 --> 00:15:45.030
So, it's going to be a long day.

191
00:15:46.430 --> 00:15:48.430
It's my job to make your job difficult.

192
00:15:48.670 --> 00:15:50.830
All of them are good enough
to be in the final 16.


193
00:15:51.070 --> 00:15:51.830
Let's begin.

194
00:16:05.150 --> 00:16:06.750
She has so much time...

195
00:16:10.150 --> 00:16:11.670
