252
00:19:03.750 --> 00:19:04.870
Please, sir. One ball.

253
00:19:06.830 --> 00:19:07.870
Just one ball.

254
00:19:08.110 --> 00:19:09.430
Thank you, my friend.

255
00:19:09.910 --> 00:19:10.830
Hello.

256
00:19:12.590 --> 00:19:13.430
Ready?

257
00:19:32.190 --> 00:19:32.990
Sir...

258
00:19:33.670 --> 00:19:34.670
One more ball, please... sir.

259
00:19:34.790 --> 00:19:35.990
- Anina.
- Please, sir.


260
00:19:37.030 --> 00:19:38.030
Was it a no-ball?

261
00:19:38.350 --> 00:19:39.310
No, right?

262
00:19:39.710 --> 00:19:40.910
